dsi_local <-
  dsi |>
  select(date, vwretd, ewretd) |>
  collect()
can_rets <-
  idx_daily |> 
  filter(gvkeyx == "000193") |> 
  window_order(datadate) |>
  mutate(ret_can = if_else(lag(prccd) > 0, prccd/lag(prccd) - 1, NA)) |> 
  filter(datadate >= "2000-01-01", datadate <= "2002-12-31") |>
  rename(date = datadate) |>
  select(date, ret_can) |>
  collect()
